title: Hundreds shut out of Guns N Roses concert in Wellington
text:
Hundreds shut out of Guns N Roses concert in Wellington Last updated 18:17, February 2 2017 BERNADETTE COURTNEY/ FAIRFAX NZ 
Guns N' Roses queuing in the rain outside Westpac Stadium, unable to get in. 
Hundreds of Guns N' Roses are gathered outside Wellington's Westpac Stadium, unable to get into the show. 
Unconfirmed reports say there is a problem with the stadium gates. 
More to come ROSS GIBLIN/ FAIRFAX NZ 
Crews set up the Guns N' Roses stage at a sodden Westpac Stadium in Wellington on Thursday. - Stuff
